Project Name: NOVA
Type: Meme Coin + In-Game Token

Vision:
NOVA is designed to become the next-generation community-driven meme coin. Our focus is on simplicity, fun, and creating an in-game economy where users can enjoy mini-games and Telegram apps while earning rewards.

Key Features:

Total Supply: 100,000,000,000 NOVA
Blockchain: TON (Telegram Open Network)

Use Cases:

Initial airdrop for community building

Purchase of in-game items (Boost, Auto Tap, Skins) with TON

Active players and holders earn NOVA rewards



Phase 1 Goals:

1. Token launch on TON


2. Community airdrop to attract holders


3. Release of the first Telegram mini-game (Tap-to-Earn or innovative mechanics)
